wp convert widget settings "MAY 2013" WordPress Codex "Function Reference"
==========================================================================

NAME
----

wp convert widget settings - Convert the widget settings from single to multi-widget format.

SYNOPSIS
--------

Convert the widget settings from single to multi-widget format.

